C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Asian%20markets%2C%20Seoul%2C%20Bangkok%20and%20Japan%20were%20trading%20in%20red.%20Whereas%20China%2C%20Jakarta%20and%20Hong%20Kong%20were%20trading%20in%20green.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20correction%20in%20the%20market%20has%20made%20largecap%20valuations%20reasonable.%20Nifty%20is%20now%20trading%20at%20around%2019%20times%20estimated%20FY%2026%20earnings.%20Therefore%2C%20long-term%20investors%2C%20who%20can%20ignore%20the%20volatility%20caused%20by%20foreign%20institutional%20investors%20(FIIs)%20selling%2C%20can%20use%20the%20dips%20to%20buy%20high%20quality%20largecaps.%20The%20bounce%20back%20of%20this%20segment%20is%20only%20a%20question%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20market%20watchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20FIIs%20sold%20equities%20worth%20Rs%204%2C341.95%20crore%20on%20January%2016%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20domestic%20institutional%20bought%20equities%20worth%20Rs%202%2C928.72%20crore%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737087300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fkjruos7_sensex_625x300_31_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsensex-declines-485-points-nifty-drops-to-23-167-in-early-trade-7492686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20stock%20market%20opened%20lower%20on%20Friday%20amid%20weak%20global%20cues%20as%20selling%20was%20seen%20in%20the%20IT%20and%20private%20bank%20sectors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsensex-declines-485-points-nifty-drops-to-23-167-in-early-trade-7492686%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20'Out%20Of%20Danger'%2C%20Attacker%20Demanded%20Rs%201%20Crore%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-attacked-intruders-entry-to-exit-what-happened-at-saif-ali-khans-home-last-night-7487262%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20sustained%20serious%20injuries%20after%20he%20was%20stabbed%20six%20times%20by%20an%20intruder%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20area%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Thursday.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20when%20the%20accused%20allegedly%20entered%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%20on%20the%2011th%20floor%20of%20the%20Satguru%20Sharan%20building%20for%20a%20burglary.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Khan's%20spinal%20fluid%20leaked%20out%20after%20shards%20of%20the%20attacker's%20knife%20lodged%20into%20his%20spine.%20According%20to%20the%20doctors%20at%20the%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20-%20where%20the%20actor%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%20-%20they%20repaired%20the%20spinal%20injury%20and%20performed%20plastic%20surgeries%20on%20the%20actor's%20hand%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20attacker's%20breaking%20in%20at%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%20lasted%20for%20nearly%2030%20minutes.%20He%20was%20first%20spotted%20in%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan's%20younger%20son%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khans-attacker-demanded-rs-1-crore-at-his-house-7488346%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeh's%20room%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJeh's%20nanny%20Eliyama%20Philip%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20same%20room%2C%20was%20the%20first%20to%20spot%20the%20intruder.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20the%20bathroom%20door%20ajar%20and%20the%20light%20on...first%20I%20assumed%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20was%20checking%20in%20on%20her%20son.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20sleep%20but%20soon%20realised%20something%20was%20wrong.%20I%20got%20up%20again%20to%20check%20when%20I%20saw%20a%20man%20come%20out%20of%20the%20bathroom%20and%20go%20into%20Jeh%20and%20Taimur's%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20nanny%20narrated.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20she%20confronted%20the%20attacker%2C%20following%20which%20he%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2056-year-old%20nanny%20tried%20to%20fight%20the%20intruder%20off%20but%20ended%20up%20suffering%20injuries%20to%20her%20wrists%20and%20hands.%20The%20second%20nanny%20who%20was%20in%20the%20same%20room%2C%20rushed%20to%20Mr%20Khan's%20room%20to%20wake%20him%20up.%20When%20Mr%20Khan%20tried%20to%20confront%20the%20intruder%2C%20he%20was%20attacked%20multiple%20times.%20The%20attacker%20immediately%20ran%20from%20the%20house%20and%20was%20later%20spotted%20near%20Bandra%20railway%20station.%20He%20likely%20took%20the%20first%20local%20train%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20the%20initial%20investigation%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khans-attacker-seen-on-cctv-in-building-staircase-7487794%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattacker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20run%2C%20possibly%20sneaked%20inside%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%20at%20some%20point%20earlier%20in%20the%20night.%20Officials%20suspect%20that%20the%20accused%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20layout%20of%20the%20building%20and%20used%20the%20shaft%20and%20stairs%20to%20reach%20the%2011th%20floor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20sections%20of%20robbery%2C%20trespassing%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bgrievous%20hurt%20caused%20while%20committing%20lurking%20house-trespass%26quot%3B.%2020%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20police%20are%20questioning%20two%20people%20who%20were%20doing%20flooring%20work%20on%20the%20terrace%20of%20the%20actor's%20house%2C%20officials%20said.%20The%20police%20have%20also%20recovered%20a%C2%A02.5-inch%20portion%20of%20a%20knife%20that%20was%20taken%20out%20from%20Mr%20Khan's%20spine.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPolice%20said%20that%20the%20suspect%20was%20last%20seen%20running%20away%20on%20the%20sixth%20floor%20of%20the%20building%20and%20was%20not%20captured%20in%20the%20lobby's%20CCTV%20cameras%20while%20entering%20or%20exiting.%20After%20the%20sixth%20floor%2C%20the%20suspect%20was%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20nor%20was%20he%20caught%20exiting%20through%20the%20main%20entrance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHours%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram%2C%20said%20that%20the%20constant%20scrutiny%20during%20an%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20challenging%20day%26quot%3B%20is%20overwhelming.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20navigate%20this%20difficult%20time%2C%20I%20respectfully%20and%20humbly%20request%20that%20the%20media%20and%20paparazzi%20refrain%20from%20the%20relentless%20speculation%20and%20coverage.%20While%20we%20appreciate%20the%20concern%20and%20support%2C%20the%20constant%20scrutiny%20and%20attention%20are%20not%20only%20overwhelming%20but%20also%20pose%20a%20significant%20risk%20to%20our%20safety.%20I%20kindly%20request%20that%20you%20respect%20our%20boundaries%20and%20give%20us%20the%20space%20we%20need%20to%20heal%20and%20cope%20as%20a%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20incident%20has%20triggered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-correct-to-call-mumbai-unsafe-devendra-fadnavis-after-saif-ali-khan-attack-7487067%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolitical%20squabble%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20BJP-led%20state%20government%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20opposition%20and%20members%20of%20the%20film%20fraternity.%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction)%20leader%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20questioned%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20celebrities%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20who%20in%20Mumbai%20is%3F%26quot%3B%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee