f%2045%20days%20or%20more%2C%20families%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20accompany%20the%20players%20for%20only%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20has%20also%20made%20playing%20domestic%20matches%20mandatory%20for%20players%20to%20be%20considered%20for%20selection%20in%20national%20teams%20or%20central%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20policy%20ensures%20that%20players%20remain%20connected%20to%20the%20domestic%20cricket%20ecosystem%2C%20fostering%20talent%20development%2C%20maintaining%20match%20fitness%2C%20and%20strengthening%20the%20overall%20domestic%20structure.%20It%20also%20inspires%20emerging%20players%20by%20providing%20them%20opportunities%20to%20compete%20alongside%20top%20cricketers%2C%20ensuring%20continuity%20in%20talent%20progression%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20policy%20document%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20exceptions%20to%20this%20mandate%20will%20be%20considered%20only%20under%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20and%20will%20require%20formal%20notification%20and%20approval%20from%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%2C%20ensuring%20fairness%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20duration%20when%20the%20families%20are%20with%20the%20players%20or%20on%20a%20tour%2C%20the%20players%20will%20travel%20together%20and%20not%20with%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20players%20are%20expected%20to%20travel%20with%20the%20team%20to%20and%20from%20matches%20and%20practice%20sessions.%20Separate%20travel%20arrangements%20with%20families%20are%20discouraged%20to%20maintain%20discipline%20and%20team%20cohesion.%20Exceptions%2C%20if%20any%2C%20must%20be%20pre-approved%20by%20the%20Head%20Coach%20and%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20putting%20restrictions%20on%20the%20players%20from%20taking%20excess%20baggage%20with%20them%2C%20the%20BCCI%20policy%20also%20puts%20restrictions%20on%20the%20use%20of%20individual%20staff%20on%20tours.%20%26quot%3BPersonal%20staff%20(e.g.%2C%20personal%20managers%2C%20chefs%2C%20assistants%2C%20and%20security)%20are%20to%20be%20restricted%20on%20tours%20or%20series%20unless%20explicitly%20approved%20by%20the%20BCCI.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20focus%20remains%20on%20team%20operations%20and%20minimizes%20logistical%20challenges.%20%E2%80%93%20this%20has%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20decided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20will%20also%20discourage%20the%20practice%20of%20players%20leaving%20training%20sessions%20early.%20They%20will%20also%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20leave%20tours%20or%20series%20midway%20unless%20it%20is%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20players%20are%20required%20to%20stay%20for%20the%20entire%20duration%20of%20scheduled%20practice%20sessions%20and%20travel%20together%20to%20and%20from%20the%20venue.%20This%20rule%20ensures%20commitment%20and%20fosters%20a%20strong%20work%20ethic%20within%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20players'%20partners%20and%20children%20(under%2018)%20will%20be%20allowed%20one%20visit%20of%20up%20to%20two%20weeks%20per%20series%20in%20case%20the%20players%20are%20absent%20from%20India%20for%20more%20than%2045%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20will%20cover%20shared%20accommodation%20with%20the%20player%20for%20the%20Visitors'%20Period%20whereas%20all%20other%20expenses%20are%20to%20be%20borne%20by%20the%20player%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20document%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20players%20are%20required%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20team%20until%20the%20scheduled%20end%20of%20the%20match%20series%20or%20tour%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20matches%20conclude%20earlier%20than%20planned.%20This%20ensures%20unity%2C%20fosters%20team%20bonding%2C%20and%20avoids%20disruption%20to%20the%20team%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20players%20are%20expected%20to%20adhere%20strictly%20to%20the%20above%20guidelines.%20Any%20exceptions%20or%20deviations%20must%20be%20pre-approved%20by%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20and%20Head%20Coach.%20Non-compliance%20may%20lead%20to%20disciplinary%20action%20as%20deemed%20appropriate%20by%20the%20BCCI.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20BCCI%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20take%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20a%20player%20which%20may%20include%20(i)%20sanction%20against%20the%20concerned%20player%20from%20participating%20in%20all%20BCCI-conducted%20tournaments%20including%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%3B%20and%20(ii)%20deduction%20from%20retainer%20amount%2Fmatch%20fees%20under%20BCCI%20Player%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737082620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fqcmgaih_sc_625x300_17_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsanctions-ipl-ban-and-bccis-big-warning-regarding-10-point-diktat-for-indian-cricket-team-stars-7490760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rattled%20by%20the%20senior%20men's%20team's%20humiliating%20debacle%20in%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20series%20against%20Australia%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20put%20in%20place%20a%20new%20policy%20for%20senior%20cricketers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsanctions-ipl-ban-and-bccis-big-warning-regarding-10-point-diktat-for-indian-cricket-team-stars-7490760%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IOC%20buys%207%20million%20barrels%20of%20Middle%20Eastern%2C%20African%20crude%20oil%20via%20tenders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737082605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fioc-buys-7-million-barrels-of-middle-eastern-african-crude-oil-via