ry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20which%20regulates%20private%20launch%20activities%2C%20said%20it%20had%20briefly%20slowed%20and%20diverted%20planes%20around%20the%20area%20where%20space%20debris%20was%20falling%2C%20but%20normal%20operations%20had%20since%20resumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20regularly%20closes%20airspace%20for%20space%20launches%20and%20reentries%2C%20but%20it%20can%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bdebris%20response%20area%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20aircraft%20from%20entering%20if%20the%20space%20vehicle%20experiences%20an%20anomaly%20outside%20the%20originally%20closed%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuccess%20is%20uncertain%2C%20but%20entertainment%20is%20guaranteed!%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20sharing%20one%20of%20the%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20just%20shared%20%26quot%3Bpreliminary%26quot%3B%20analysis%20about%20what%20might%20have%20caused%20the%20Starship%20spacecraft%20to%20fail%20roughly%2010%20minutes%20into%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreliminary%20indication%20is%20that%20we%20had%20an%20oxygen%2Ffuel%20leak%20in%20the%20cavity%20above%20the%20ship%20engine%20firewall%20that%20was%20large%20enough%20to%20build%20pressure%20in%20excess%20of%20the%20vent%20capacity.%20Apart%20from%20obviously%20double-checking%20for%20leaks%2C%20we%20will%20add%20fire%20suppression%20to%20that%20volume%20and%20probably%20increase%20vent%20area.%20Nothing%20so%20far%20suggests%20pushing%20next%20launch%20past%20next%20month%26quot%3B%2C%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20SpaceX%20launch%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos's%20owned%20Blue%20Origin's%20massive%20New%20Glenn%20rocket%20reached%20orbital%20space%20for%20the%20first%20time%20overnight%2C%20marking%20a%20potential%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20commercial%20space%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737082500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9ufqot8_spacex-starship