0sending%20pedestrians%20running%20from%20the%20scene.%20After%20striking%20the%20barriers%2C%20the%20truck%20backed%20up%20in%20reverse%2C%20then%20lurched%20forward%2C%20striking%20the%20metal%20barriers%20a%20second%20time.%20The%20second%20impact%20disabled%20the%20truck%20which%20began%20smoking%20from%20the%20engine%20compartment%20and%20leaking%20fluids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKandula%20next%20exited%20the%20vehicle%20and%20went%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20truck.%20From%20a%20backpack%20he%20removed%20a%20flag%2C%20a%20three-by-five%20foot%20red-and-white%20banner%20with%20a%20Nazi%20Swastika%20in%20the%20centre%2C%20and%20brandished%20it.%20US%20Park%20Police%20and%20the%20US%20Secret%20Service%20officers%20arrested%20Kandula%20at%20the%20scene%20and%20took%20him%20into%20custody%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20plea%20agreement%2C%20at%20the%20time%20Kandula%20crashed%20the%20truck%20into%20the%20White%20House%20perimeter%2C%20he%20was%20attempting%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20White%20House%20to%20seize%20political%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKandula's%20intent%20was%20to%20replace%20the%20democratically%20elected%20government%20with%20a%20dictatorship%20fueled%20by%20ideology%20of%20Nazi%20Germany%20and%20for%20himself%20to%20be%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20Kandula%20admitted%20to%20investigators%20that%20he%20would%20have%20arranged%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20US%20President%20and%20others%20if%20necessary%20to%20achieve%20his%20objective.%20His%20actions%20were%20calculated%20to%20influence%20or%20affect%20the%20conduct%20of%20government%20by%20intimidation%20or%20coercion%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20his%20actions%20caused%20USD%204%2C322%20in%20damage%20to%20the%20National%20Park%20Service.%20This%20amount%20included%20costs%20for%20repairing%20the%20metal%20bollard%20barriers%20to%20their%20original%20condition%20and%20ensuring%20structural%20soundness%2C%20oil%20and%20chemical%20removal%2C%20spill%20cleanup%2C%20and%20disposal%20of%20fluids%20from%20the%20crashed%20U-Haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKandula%20planned%20the%20attack%20for%20several%20weeks.%20Prior%20to%20renting%20the%20truck%20and%20crashing%20it%20on%20the%20White%20House%20grounds%2C%20he%20made%20several%20attempts%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20vehicles%20or%20armed%20security%20guards.%20For%20example%2C%20on%20April%2022%2C%202023%2C%20Kandula%20requested%2025%20armed%20guards%20and%20an%20armoured%20convoy%20from%20a%20security%20company%20located%20in%20Virginia%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%204%2C%202023%2C%20Kandula%20attempted%20to%20contact%20several%20other%20companies%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20rent%20a%20large%20commercial%20tractor-trailer%20truck%2C%20a%20dump%20truck%2C%20or%20another%20large%20truck.%20Kandula%20was%20unsuccessful%20in%20arraigning%20for%20security%20guards%20or%20a%20tractor-trailer%20truck%20or%20dump%20truck.%20Kandula%20had%20attempted%20to%20arrange%20for%20the%20services%20of%20these%20security%20guards%20and%20the%20use%20of%20large%20vehicles%20in%20order%20to%20carry%20out%20his%20offense%20against%20the%20US%20government%2C%20a%20media%20release%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737080700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fh37io6n8_sai-varshith-kandula_625x300_17_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsai-varshith-kandula-indian-origin-man-gets-8-years-jail-for-attempted-attack-on-white-house-7492113%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20national%20Sai%20Varshith%20Kandula%2C%2020%2C%20on%20Thursday%20was%20sentenced%20to%20eight%20years%20for%20an%20at