0ban%2C%20%246.17%20billion%20to%20%248.64%20billion%20of%20ad%20spending%20could%20need%20a%20new%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20social%20media%20giant's%20loss%20could%20be%20another%20social%20media%20giant's%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20estimated%20that%20Meta%2C%20owner%20of%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%2C%20could%20reap%20anywhere%20between%20%242.46%20billion%20to%20%243.38%20billion%20in%20ad%20revenue%20with%20a%20TikTok%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Tiktok%20and%20Meta%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20say%20that%20Meta%20will%20be%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3Blargest%20fundamental%20winner%20of%20any%20TikTok%20ban%26quot%3B%20in%20part%20due%20to%20its%20existing%20user%20base%20and%20data%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20could%20add%205%20to%209%20percent%20in%20Meta's%20earnings%20per%20share%20for%20the%202026%20fiscal%20year%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Escrolling%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20also%20poised%20to%20replace%20some%20of%20the%20time%20US%20users%20spent%20on%20TikTok%2C%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEMARKETER%3C%2Fspan%3E%20estimates%20that%20TikTok%20users%20in%20the%20US%20spent%20nearly%20an%20hour%20of%20their%20day%20on%20the%20app%20in%202024%20and%20nearly%20three%20quarters%20of%20those%20users%20were%20also%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20leaves%20close%20to%20an%20hour%20of%20their%20daily%20media%20time%20up%20for%20grabs%2C%26quot%3B%20eMarketer%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20say%20that%20Meta%20would%20gain%20around%20%24.30%20to%20%24.60%20to%20their%202026%20earnings%20per%20share%20estimates%20for%20every%2010%25%20of%20TikTok's%20US%20time%20Meta%20captures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upside%20of%20a%20TikTok%20ban%20won't%20be%20concentrated%20to%20Meta.%3