0brisket).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20though%2C%20they%20said%20the%20pulled%20pork%20was%20a%20safe%20bet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20kept%20my%20la%20Barbecue%20order%20simple.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221891%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bowl%20of%20beans%2C%20container%20of%20pickles%2C%20and%20pile%20of%20food%20at%20La%20Barbecue%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67813fb88951662c9f1f978a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20order%20at%20la%20Barbecue%20consisted%20of%20a%20serving%20of%20pulled%20pork%20and%20two%20sides.%20%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Stinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20pulled%20pork%20with%20a%20side%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeans-could-be-secret-for-living-longer-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblack%20beans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20house-made%20garlic%20pickles.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pork%20was%20cooked%20quite%20nicely%20with%20a%20strong%20pepper%20seasoning%2C%20and%20the%20garlic%20pickles%20tasted%20fresh%20and%20had%20a%20nice%20kick.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beans%20were%20perfectly%20fine%2C%20but%20didn't%20strike%20me%20as%20a%20side%20I'd%20order%20again.%20I'd%20definitely%20order%20the%20pulled%20pork%20again%2C%20though.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELeRoy%20and%20Lewis%20Barbecue%20had%20a%20large%20space%20complete%20with%20a%20full%20bar.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221891%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20of%20LeRoy%20and%20Lewis%20barbecue%20joint%20with%20counter%20and%20menu%20sign%20above%20it%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67813fbd88b000981b4a5c23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOrdering%20was%20a%20breeze%20at%20LeRoy%20and%20Lewis.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Stinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELeRoy%20and%20Lewis%20Barbecue%20was%20a%20popular%