20that%20players%20remain%20connected%20to%20the%20domestic%20cricket%20ecosystem%2C%20fostering%20talent%20development%2C%20maintaining%20match%20fitness%2C%20and%20strengthening%20the%20overall%20domestic%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20stated%20Any%20exceptions%20to%20this%20mandate%20will%20require%20formal%20notification%20and%20approval%20from%20Agarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20this%20instruction%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20stars%20from%20the%20Ranji%20ciruit.%20Virat%20Kohli%20hasn't%20played%20a%20Ranji%20Trophy%20match%20since%202012%2C%20that%20was%20one%20year%20before%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20played%20his%20last%20Ranji%20match%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbattled%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20last%20played%20Ranji%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlayers%20Traveling%20Separately%20with%20Families%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20travel%20with%20the%20team%20to%20and%20from%20matches%20and%20practice%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20said%20that%20separate%20travel%20arrangements%20with%20families%20are%20being%20discouraged%20to%20maintain%20%26quot%3Bdiscipline%20and%20team%20cohesion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExceptions%2C%20if%20any%2C%20must%20be%20pre-approved%20by%20Gambhir%20and%20Agarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20after%20one%20superstar%20player%20travelled%20separately%20on%20tours%2C%20including%20last%20year%20during%20the%20South%20Africa%20assignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20big%20stars%2C%20during%20the%20recent%20tour%20of%20Australia%2C%20refused%20to%20travel%20with%20teams%20and%20one%20of%20them%20hired%20a%20charter%20flight%20for%20travelling%20from%20one%20Australian%20city%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExcess%20Baggage%20Limit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers%20would%20now%20be%20required%20to%20adhere%20to%20specified%20baggage%20limits%20shared%20with%20the%20team.%20Any%20excess%20baggage%20co