le-is-the-deal-13290273%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trump%20vs%20China%20Trade%20War%20Fallout%20Has%20Dealt%20A%20Blow%20To%20'Make%20In%20India'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20manufacturing%20industry%20is%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20a%20fallout%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20over%20threats%20of%20a%20trade%20and%20tariff%20war%20by%20the%20incoming%20Trump%20administration%2C%20and%20its%20retaliatory%20measures%20imposed%20by%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20under%20its%20flagship%20'Make%20in%20India'%20programme%2C%20India%20has%20seen%20exponential%20growth%20in%20key%20sectors%20like%20solar%20power%2C%20electronics%20and%20mobile%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20the%20automobile%20sector%2C%20especially%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20or%20EVs%20-%20all%20of%20which%20are%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20dependent%20on%20raw%20materials%2C%20components%2C%20and%20ancillaries%20supplied%20by%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20China%20prepares%20for%20an%20imminent%20face-off%20with%20the%20US%2C%20which%20may%20be%20just%20days%20away%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%20as%20President%20on%20January%2020%2C%20Beijing%20has%20already%20made%20the%20first%20move%20by%20taking%20some%20precautionary%20measures%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20Washington%20that%20it%20too%20will%20suffer%20the%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20put%20restrictions%20on%20the%20export%20of%20key%20raw%20materials%2C%20essential%20rare%20earth%20minerals%2C%20components%2C%20high-tech%20equipment%2C%20and%20machinery%20which%20are%20needed%20to%20manufacture%20solar%20panels%2C%20its%20parts%2C%20mobile%20phones%20and%20other%20gadgets%2C%20as%20well%20as%20EVs%20and%20its%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20curbs%20not%20just%20pertain%20to%20direct%20exports%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20to%20any%20other%20country%20which%20uses%20them%20to%20manufacture%20finished%20products%20meant%20to%20be%20shipped%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202024%2C%20China%20banned%20the%20export%20of%20gallium%20and%20germanium%2C%20which%20are%20vital%20for%20solar%20cell%20production.%20Shortly%20after%20that%2C%20it%20also%20banned%20antimony%2C%20critical%20for%20semiconductors%20and%20essential%20defence%20technologies.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Beijing%20further%20declared%20that%20it%20will%20now%20add%20lithium%20extraction%20and%20battery%20cathode%20technologies%20-%20which%20are%20crucial%20for%20EV%20battery%20manufacturing%20-%20to%20its%20controlled%20export%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20US%20having%20reduced%20its%20dependence%20on%20China%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20its%20overall%20imports%2C%20Washington%20has%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20increasingly%20turned%20to%20New%20Delhi%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20Beijing%20to%20fill%20the%20deficit.%20And%20so%2C%20China's%20latest%20curbs%2C%20though%20aimed%20at%20the%20US%2C%20has%20indirectly%20hurt%20India%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20firms%20in%20electronics%2C%20solar%2C%20and%20EV%20sectors%20are%20facing%20major%20delays%20and%20disruptions%20as%20China%20has%20blocked%20exports%20of%20inputs%20and%20machinery%2C%26quot%3B%20economic%20think-tank%20GTRI%20founder%20Ajay%20Srivastava%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20China's%20export%20restrictions%2C%20as%20many%20of%20its%20industries%20depend%20on%20Chinese%20machinery%2C%20intermediate%20goods%2C%20and%20components.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20also%20signals%20deeper%20geopolitical%20tensions%20and%20trade%20war.%20We%20hope%20India-specific%20restrictions%20go%20away%20soon%20as%20they%20will%20also%20hurt%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20imports%20from%20China%20increased%20to%20%24101.73%20billion%20in%202023-24%20from%20%2498.5%20billion%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20think-tank%20even%20suggested%20that%20China's%20moves%20may%20be%20double-edged%2C%20as%20Beijing%20has%20been%20displeased%20for%20a%20while%20over%20New%20Delhi's%20restrictions%20on%20Chinese%20investments%20and%20visas%20for%20its%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20deadly%20Galwan%20Valley%20clash%20between%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20soldiers%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20had%20made%20it%20mandatory%20for%20countries%20sharing%20land%20borders%20with%20India%20to%20seek%20its%20approval%20for%20investments%20in%20any%20sector.%20The%20move%20was%20also%20made%20keeping%20in%20mind%20India's%20national%20security%20objectives%20in%20its%20volatile%20neighbourhood.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737039960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Ffqgc205o_trump-xi-g20-meet-osaka-june-2019-_625x300_06_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-donald-trump-vs-china-trade-war-fallout-has-dealt-a-blow-to-make-in-india-7489494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20manufacturing%20industry%20is%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20a%20fallout%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20over%20threats%20of%20a%20trade%20and%20tariff%20war%20by%20the%20incoming%20Trump%20administration%2C%20and%20its%20retaliatory%20measures%20imposed%20by%20Beijing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-donald-trump-vs-china-trade-war-fallout-has-dealt-a-blow-to-make-in-india-7489494%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%2015%20Months%20Of%20War%2C%20What%20A%20Ceasefire%20Deal%20Would%20Mean%20For%20People%20Of%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Middle%20East%20has%20witnessed%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20marking%20a%20potential%20end%20to%2015%20months%20of%20bloodshed%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20This%20development%20comes%20after%20intense%20diplomatic%20efforts%2C%20with%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20describing%20the%20negotiations%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20toughest%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20ever%20encountered.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20agreement%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Egypt%2C%20and%20Qatar%2C%20outlines%20a%20three-stage%20process%20aimed%20at%20restoring%20calm%20to%20the%20war-torn%20region.%20The%20initial%20phase%2C%20expected%20to%20last%20approximately%20six%20weeks%2C%20will%20see%20a%20gradual%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20release%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20held%20by%20Hamas%2C%20and%20the%20release%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20detained%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20must%20now%20secure%20approval%20from%20his%20security%20Cabinet%20and%20full%20Cabinet%20before%20the%20deal%20can%20proceed.%20However%2C%20Netanyahu's%20office%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Israeli%20cabinet%20would%20not%20convene%20to%20vote%20on%20the%20deal%20until%20mediators%20are%20notified%20that%20Hamas%20has%20accepted%20all%20elements%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20according%20to%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20then%20have%2024%20hours%20to%20permit%20an%20appeal%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20ceasefire%20to%20take%20effect.%20While%20the%20exact%20timeline%20is%20uncertain%2C%20the%20truce%20is%20expected%20to%20commence%20on%20Sunday%2C%20provided%20all%20necessary%20approvals%20are%20obtained%2C%20per%20NBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%20is%20implemented%2C%20attention%20will%20turn%20to%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20negotiations%2C%20expected%20to%20commence%20within%2016%20days.%20This%20stage%20will%20focus%20on%20securing%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20release%20of%20remaining%20hostages%2C%20and%20the%20full%20withdrawal%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20it%20impact%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20remains%20dire%2C%20with%20over%2046%2C500%20people%20killed%20and%201.9%20million%20displaced.%20The%20agreement%20stipulates%20that%20at%20least%20600%20truckloads%20of%20aid%20will%20be%20allowed%20into%20Gaza%20daily%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20portion%20allocated%20to%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20been%20severely%20affected%20by%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20deal%20will%20bring%20relief%20to%20Gaza%20as%20they%20have%20faced%2015%20months%20of%20deadly%20airstrikes%20and%20displacement%20without%20any%20aid.%20It%20will%20also%20see%20Israeli%20forces%20retreating%20from%20central%20Gaza%20and%20will%20permit%20Palestinians%20who%20have%20been%20displaced%20to%20return%20to%20the%20area%20to%20start%20finding%20loved%20ones%20gone%20missing%20or%20feared%20buried%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20governed%20Gaza%20since%202007%2C%20they%20would%20probably%20have%20to%20rebuild%20with%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20brother%20Mohammed%20as%20the%20new%20leader%2C%20and%20since%20it%20has%20not%20been%20expelled%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20alternate%20to%20its%20governance%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20and%20the%20operations%20related%20to%20reconstruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20survival%20and%20continued%20influence%20in%20the%20region%20will%20likely%20depend%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20navigate%20the%20complex%20web%20of%20international%20diplomacy%20and%20provide%20for%20the%20basic%20needs%20of%20the%20Gaza%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20way%20forward%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20community%2C%20particularly%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Egypt%2C%20and%20Qatar%2C%20will%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20agreement%20holds.%20These%20countries%20will%20act%20as%20guarantors%2C%20providing%20diplomatic%20support%20and%20oversight%20to%20facilitate%20a%20lasting%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20left%20deep%20scars%2C%20and%20the%20road%20to%20recovery%20will%20be%20long%20and%20challenging.%20As%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20look%20to%20the%20future%2C%20they%20do%20so%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20hope%20and%20skepticism.%20The%20agreement%2C%20while%20promising%2C%20is%20fragile%20and%20requires%20careful%20nurturing%20to%20ensure%20its%20success.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737039180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ffa252p1_israelhamas-war_625x300_16_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-15-months-of-war-what-a-ceasefire-deal-would-mean-for-people-of-gaza-7489399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20deal%20will%20bring%20relief%20to%20Gaza%20as%20they%20have%20faced%2015%20months%20of%20deadly%20airstrikes%20and%20displacement%20without%20any%20aid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-15-months-of-war-what-a-ceasefire-deal-would-mean-for-people-of-gaza-7489399%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20drone%20shot%20down%20near%20presidential%20palace%20during%20PM's%20Ukraine%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737034020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F01%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-keir-starmer-volodymyr-zelenskyy_6801299.jpg%3F20250116134718%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussian-drone-shot-down-near-presidential-palace-during-starmers-ukraine-visit-13290189%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2